Limpopo police seeks assistance with information of the whereabouts of a step mother who on Wednesday morning plucked off step-son s eyes.According to close sources, the child aged 4 woke up crying complaining about hunger and the raged step mother took sharp bottles and plucked off the poor child s eyes. This is cruelty to humanity, the boy was crying since 5am complaining about hunger, we suspect that he slept with an empty stomach. The woman had many cases of child abuse but no one formed the authorities. We want to thank the councilor for taking the child to the hospital and catering for all the medical bills he said.The father of the son couldn t be reached for a comment.The current condition of the child is unknown but rumor has it that he is stable and the eyesight might not be restored.CLICK NEXT TO SEE IMAGE